title: What is no one talking about?
itunes:title: What is no one talking about?
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down the latest NFL news, including Ryan Fitzpatrick signing a new deal with the Jets and the chances Paxton Lynch will start for the Broncos. Then, the heroes discuss some under the radar storylines before wrapping the podcast reading more iTunes comments!
